sequenceDiagram
actor User
participant Browser
participant View as SpisTresciView
participant Search as search_models()
participant Manager as SearchableManager
participant DB as Database

User->>Browser: Enter query "q"
Browser->>View: GET /spis_tresci/?q=...
View->>Search: search_models(query_text, [Piosenka])
Search->>Manager: Piosenka.objects.search(query_text)
Manager->>DB: full-text search (tsvector)
DB-->>Manager: matching songs
Manager-->>Search: results with rank/snippets
Search-->>View: results_by_app
View-->>Browser: render song list
Browser-->>User: displays categorized songs